user_text: 관중 수 상위 10개 팀의 최근 리그 순위를 분석해줘
sql: SELECT gi.game_date, g.team_abbreviation_home, g.team_abbreviation_away, gi.attendance FROM game_info AS gi JOIN game AS g ON g.game_id = gi.game_id ORDER BY gi.attendance DESC LIMIT 10
SELECT display_first_last, season_exp, from_year, to_year FROM common_player_info WHERE season_exp >= 0 LIMIT 200
